oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Portrait, Louis E. Trice, II
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Portrait in a cardboard frame, Louis E. Trice, II. Louis was born in Dallas, Texas to Louis E. Trice and Eura Parmer Trice in 1914. His father was born and raised in Montgomery County, Tennessee. On verso, "To my dear cousin Ethel. From Louis Trice 12/25/45".
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Portraits
